These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, rabbit, goat
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, apricot, azure, chestnut
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, scrabble, bridge
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby, skiing
 1. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the person who likes azure is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person playing bridge##2
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who likes azure and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person who likes chestnut is the owner of the goat##1
13. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing chess and the owner of the rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Pet         | hamster  | hedgehog      | rabbit   | goat     |
| Color           | apricot | aquamarine | azure   | chestnut     |
| Game   | chess    | scrabble         | snooker | bridge         |
| Sport         | skiing     | baseball     | climbing  | rugby       |

