The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
House: townhouse, futuristic, cape-cod, palace
4 different games are played: domino, whist, scrabble, canasta
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the person playing whist is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person playing whist is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the townhouse house is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
11. the townhouse house is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
